init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He starts to get worried and calls his wife, who is in the kitchen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He tries to call his friends, but they all say the same thing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He starts to call the police to report this, but they say that they can't help him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They go to the store where they bought the mugs and talk to the manager.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He says he has no idea.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They tell the news station about the mugs and they say they will send a reporter.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Jane was interviewing Tom when all of a sudden the mug changes again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She said this was the biggest story she had ever covered.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The next day the news station had a special report on the changing mugs.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They said that they had discovered that the mugs were changing because of a new type of coffee called "The New Dad."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: of a signal that was being sent from a satellite.
